---
/**
 * @fileoverview Logout Page
 *
 * Client-side logout page that clears the user session via API
 * and redirects to the login page. Shows a loading spinner during
 * the logout process.
 *
 * @module pages/logout/index
 * @see {@link module:lib/auth/api-client} - Logout function
 * @see {@link module:pages/api/auth/logout} - Logout API
 * @see {@link module:pages/login/index} - Redirect destination
 *
 * ## Route
 *
 * `/logout/` - Public (handles both authenticated and unauthenticated)
 *
 * ## Behavior
 *
 * 1. Page loads with "Logging out..." message and spinner
 * 2. Calls `logout()` from api-client to clear session
 * 3. Redirects to `/login/` after completion
 *
 * ## UI Elements
 *
 * - Centered loading spinner (CSS animation)
 * - "Logging out..." text
 * - No navigation or other controls
 *
 * @author How To Win Capitalism Team
 * @since 1.0.0
 */
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Logging Out... | How To Win Capitalism</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      background: #fff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .message {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .spinner {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border: 3px solid #eee;
      border-top-color: #0066cc;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    }

    @keyframes spin {
      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="message">
    <div class="spinner"></div>
    <p>Logging out...</p>
  </div>

  <script>
    import { logout } from '../../lib/auth/api-client';

    // Clear auth state via API
    async function performLogout() {
      await logout();
      window.location.href = '/login/';
    }

    performLogout();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
